### Переменные
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3033

### ========================================
### TEMPLATES
### ========================================

### GET - Получить все templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates

### POST - Создать новый template
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Заявление на отпуск",
  "filePath": "/templates/system/vacation-request.docx",
  "variables": ["employeeName", "startDate", "endDate", "position"],
  "storageType": "system",
  "mimeType": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document"
}

### POST - Создать user template
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Пользовательский шаблон",
  "filePath": "/templates/user/custom-doc.docx",
  "variables": ["title", "content", "author"],
  "storageType": "user",
  "userId": "user123",
  "mimeType": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document"
}
